VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT org\.apache\.poi\.hssf\.usermodel\.HSSFWorkbook
WHEN EXPR MISSING:XSSFWorkbook|validate|allowlist && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the use of HSSFWorkbook for Excel file manipulation, which may expose applications to vulnerabilities due to outdated libraries.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Package: org.apache.poi.hssf.usermodel.HSSFWorkbook.
